XSBC-Original-Maintainer: Ricardo Mones <mones@debian.org>
Build-Depends: dpkg-dev (>= 1.14.8), debhelper (>> 5), libdb-dev, libgnutls-dev, liblockfile-dev, libsasl2-dev, libexpat1-dev, libcurl4-gnutls-dev (>= 7.16.4-5)
